{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回\"弄巧反拙\"中，小鱼儿与铁心兰被小仙女张菁追上。小鱼儿先前伪装成糟老头被小仙女识破，双方展开追逐。小仙女掌法奇快无比，将小鱼儿打得遍体鳞伤，但小鱼儿凭药水泡大的铜筋铁骨顽强不倒。他故意示弱装死，再以激将法惹怒小仙女，趁其不备突然出手将其制服，反过来狠狠教训了小仙女一顿，最终饶了她。铁心兰向小鱼儿讲述小仙女抢藏宝图的原因——其母\"玉娘子\"张三娘痴恋昔日第一剑客燕南天，而藏宝图正是燕南天入恶人谷前所留，藏有无敌剑谱。途中神秘黑衣人黑蜘蛛现身，自称轻功天下第一，想与小鱼儿交朋友。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "孩子的妈，你哭什么，又死不了的，快去找大夫吧，再迟人家只怕就要关起门来睡大觉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说完了么？不错，你装得很像，你此刻真该去找大夫了，只可惜世上所有的大夫都已救不了你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还有什么活说？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "很好，终于被你瞧破了，但你是如何瞧出来的？可否说来听听？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我砍下那一刀时，风声连聋子都听得出，你若真是个糟老头子，早已骇得仆倒在地，又怎会还是若无其事地往前走？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "不错，原来你也是个聪明人，聪明得出乎我意料之外。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你现在才知道，不嫌太迟了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "但你也莫要神气，我总算还是骗过你一阵子，你发觉得才真的是太迟了，我若不是身旁有个累赘，早已不知走到哪里去了，还会等着被你追上！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你既然那么聪明，此刻就该还能再想出个法子逃走……你若想不出，可见你的脑袋还是没有用，不如割下来也罢。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "我何必再想什么法子？你以为我真的打不过你？我先前只不过是懒得和你动手罢了，常言道，好男不与女斗，我……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "住手，好男不跟女斗，住手！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "住手，住手，你已中了我的毒，你……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你不相信？你可知我这毒药有多厉害？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "在我手下，天下可说绝无一人还能抽出手来施毒，何况是你这小鬼，你又想骗我，你简直是做梦！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "我不骗你，我……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鱼儿，你……你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你放心，她打不死我的，只要她打不死我，我总能打倒她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，我倒要看看你骨头有多硬。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "算了吧，求求你……你打不过她，她实在太快了！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "就因为她太快，所以打不死我……出手太快，就不会太重，这道理你难道不明白？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，算你骨头硬，我倒要瞧瞧你的骨头有多硬！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你只要服输，我就饶了你！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "放屁！谁要你饶我……要你求我饶你……我要扒下你的衣裳，把你吊在树上，狠狠地抽你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鬼！小坏种！小流氓！你还能站起来么？你还能再打么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你才是坏种！流氓！你……你还是强盗……",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还敢骂我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你……你……你好狠，人家已躺在地上，你还要动手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "谁叫这小鬼骂我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "我骂你，我偏要骂你，你见财起意、你无恶不作、你杀人如草、你……你是见鬼的小仙女，你简直是个母夜叉。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，你骂，你骂……我叫你永远再也骂不出，我本不想杀你，这是你逼我的，我……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鱼儿，你……你这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我早就告诉过你，她打不死我的……我这身子是被药水泡大的，别人吃奶的时候，我就已开始吃药……莫说是她，就算是出手比她再重十倍的人，也休想将我打得真个爬不起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你……你方才……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我方才只是故意装出来骗她的，好叫她不防备，然后再故意骂她，让她生气，她气晕了头，我就笑歪了嘴。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你真的没事么？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我这一身铜筋铁骨，凭她那两只又白又嫩的小手能伤得了我？她拳头打在我身上，简直好像在弹棉花似的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "现在你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你哭也没有用的，我说过要还你几拳，就是要还你几拳，一拳也不会少……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你求我饶你，我就少打几拳。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这恶贼，你打死我吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你就饶了她吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "饶她！我为什么要饶她，她方才为何不饶我，我说过要扒下她的衣服，将她吊在树上……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你敢！你若真的，我……我死了也不饶你！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你活着我尚不怕，何况死的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "这是本钱，先还你，还要再加利息。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你好狠……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "我狠？你自己难道不狠？……你只知别人对你出手狠，难道就忘了你对别人出手时，岂非还要比这狠得多。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这恶狗、恶魔……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你若骂得好，我听听也没关系，还觉有趣，但你实在不会骂人，骂人的技术你一点也不懂，我只有请你住嘴了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "求求你……饶了我吧……饶了我吧……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "好，你终于求我饶你了，你莫要忘记。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我饶了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白菜兄，这次辛苦了你，背我们两人一程吧，到了前面，我一定好好请你吃一顿，还得喝两杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "小仙女，再见了……嗯，还是莫要再见的好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你真的是张箐的灾星。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "她遇见我，算她倒楣。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我真没想到，你真的打起来时，竟那么狠，那么不怕死……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我也许是个坏蛋，但却绝不是孬种。别人想要我于什么都容易，但谁也休想叫我求饶。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，你就算坏，但也坏得是个男子汉。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可知道'小仙女'张菁为什么要抢我那张藏宝图？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "还不是见财起意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那你就错了，她手段虽然毒辣，却不是个坏人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "她难道是好人？……好人要杀你，坏人却救了你，这岂非怪事！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我跟你说正经的，她要抢我的藏宝图，只因为她母亲和这批宝藏的主人有很密切的关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "哦！……她已经这么凶了，她母亲岂非更是个母夜叉。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她母亲非但不是个母夜叉，还是昔日江湖中一位大大有名的美人，只要看见过她的男人，没有一个不被她迷得要死要活的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这样的人，我倒想瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只可惜你迟生了几年，她现在已经老了，但江湖中老一辈的人听到'玉娘子'张三娘的名字，心还会直跳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你为什么不说只可惜她早生了几年，见不着我……那么，小仙女的父亲又是个何许人物？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这……这我却不清楚。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不错，有名美人的子女，的确有许多是找不到父亲的，只因为可能是她父亲的人太多了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你少缺德，那'玉娘子'虽然美得如玉．但也冷得如冰，江湖中追求她的男人虽不知有多少，但她瞧得上的却只有一个。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "谁有如此艳福？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "就是那藏珍的主人，名叫燕南天！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "燕南天！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你也听过这名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我……我好像听见过，却已记不清了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若听到过这名字，就不该忘记。他本是昔日江湖中最最有名的剑客，他的剑法，至今还没有一个人能比得上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他生得虽不英俊，但却是江湖中最有男人气概的男子汉，只可惜我也迟生了几年，见不着他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你可要我帮你找他？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你已找不着他，任何人都找不着他，江湖传言，十几年前，他不知为了什么，闯入'恶人谷'，从此就没有再出来，他虽然剑法无敌，但遇着那许多恶人，只怕……还是难逃毒手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "噢……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这藏宝图，据说就是他入谷之前留下的，他似乎也自知入谷之后必死，所以便将他生前搜集的古玩珍宝，以及他无敌天下的剑谱，全都藏在一个隐密之处，若没有这藏宝图，谁也找不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "珍宝虽不足令人动心，但这剑谱却的确令人眼红，谁得了这剑谱，谁就可无敌于天下，那就难怪有这许多人要来抢了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但小仙女却非为这剑谱，而是为了要安慰她的母亲……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你瞧，这……这是……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我早就瞧见了，地上的影子，已多了一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你怕什么，我若要取你们性命，早已出手了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若害怕，早已跳下马了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，你这人很有意思，我早就瞧出你很有意思，想交交你这朋友，所以才跟着来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫非就是黑蜘蛛？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不错，你居然认得我。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你怎会到这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我本也是为你来的，但瞧见这小伙子，觉得很有趣，可真比那藏宝图有趣多了，我想交这朋友，只好放弃那藏宝图。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到居然会有人将我瞧得比这藏宝图还重，这种朋友我也要交的……只是，黑蜘蛛，这又算什么名字？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你连黑蜘蛛这名字都未听过，简直是孤陋寡闻，当今天下，不知我名字的人，还能在江湖中混么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你什么时候跟上我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你将白马涂成花马时，我就瞧见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，我竟不知道。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我若存心要跟住一个人，就算跟上一辈子，那人也不会知道。我若不愿被人瞧见，当今天下，又有谁能够瞧见我的影子？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你年纪虽小，口气可真不小。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "谁说我年纪小？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我听你说话，难道还听不出？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我年纪纵然小，也大得可以做你叔叔伯伯了，只是我既想交你这朋友，也不愿倚老卖老，你就叫我大哥吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    }
  ],
